{
  "stem": "10745.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans taught me how to shoot a gun, a rifle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just hit me by the shoulder very hard, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He showed me how to take it apart, put it together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he said-- because we could commute-- OK, it's German-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it's not the same-- but we commute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They understood us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We understood them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the German said to me-- he said to my father, not to me, but I was there-- he said to my father, he said, why did you remain?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't understand why he meant-- why we remained, we didn't go back with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they left, because the front went fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then came in only a few Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't see too many Germans walking the-- we only had one street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's say a street and a half.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Germans came in, only a few.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they organized the worst Ukrainians they could find-- murderers or anything else, just the worst guys they could find-- to make police.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first thing the Germans demanded was all the gold and silver, any valuable thing from the Jews to give away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They came in and took whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they roughed it up and everything else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was one time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then the second time, they said anyone who had any livestock or any living creature in a Jewish home, they cannot have them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a cow, we had chickens, we had ducks, we had all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a big barn in the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a whole underground tunnel which we used to keep potatoes and everything else for the winter times.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we used to prepare it and save for the winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
